issue.title: [CF 997] Burst of Speed not displayed in SpeedBoosts
issue.body:
First - sorry for my bad english
The problem is Rogue talent Burst of Speed not displayed in SpeedBoosts
his id in SpeedBoosts is 108212, but for some reasons his real id is 137573 - http://www.wowhead.com/spell=137573
im using latest RUSSIAN version at this moment
and w\o SpeedBoosts id 108212 doesnt work too


> Posted by CurseForge user joyeee | Imported from CurseForge issue #997 | Raw

comments.body:
Fixed in g5150971. Thanks for the report.

In the meantime, you can just type "SpeedBoosts; 137573" for the spells to track to track it properly.

Edited Sep 18, 2014

> Posted by CurseForge user Cybeloras
